27#include <util.h>
28
29#include <libyasm.h>
30
31
32yasm_dbgfmt_module yasm_null_LTX_dbgfmt;
33
34
35static /*@null@*/ /*@only@*/ yasm_dbgfmt *
36null_dbgfmt_create(yasm_object *object)
37{
38 yasm_dbgfmt_base *dbgfmt = yasm_xmalloc(sizeof(yasm_dbgfmt_base));
39 dbgfmt->module = &yasm_null_LTX_dbgfmt;
40 return (yasm_dbgfmt *)dbgfmt;
41}
42
43static void
44null_dbgfmt_destroy(/*@only@*/ yasm_dbgfmt *dbgfmt)
45{
46 yasm_xfree(dbgfmt);
47}
48
49static void
50null_dbgfmt_generate(yasm_object *object, yasm_linemap *linemap,
51 yasm_errwarns *errwarns)
52{
53}
54
55
56/* Define dbgfmt structure -- see dbgfmt.h for details */
57yasm_dbgfmt_module yasm_null_LTX_dbgfmt = {
58 "No debugging info",
59 "null",
60 NULL, /* no directives */
61 null_dbgfmt_create,
62 null_dbgfmt_destroy,
63 null_dbgfmt_generate
64};
